---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="İletişim | Solut Enerji"
  description="Güneş enerjisi, EV şarj ve danışmanlık çözümleri için Solut Enerji uzman ekibiyle iletişime geçin."
>
  <section class="relative flex min-h-[320px] items-center overflow-hidden bg-primary pb-0 pt-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20">
      <img
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        alt="Mühendisler çalışırken"
        src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDJmz9PyFKBk46eG2SXqAshAHV1O56k44mvhK5_EH33ukaj4pdQzul0_Z5IvdEO0nwIqbKn7tP2dx1q-1XpdRprMe3z3Gj14qP1RDg0iWsY71Q-CHtHGM3YrbvQ9Ld3dLieSwL8KbYVkkhLvdCrciv0pqK6-BbDqCyIAeukZXMPNHmjVHxwuYB1mLGo6aXTsRMemgh4NCD18tmIQIoI6AVlW-2isUTx3GDTaplCSKuyk-BspToHHAxHSYrTOiwBu166XL6GlByvdiA"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-20">
      <span class="mb-4 block text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary-container">
        Bizimle İletişime Geçin
      </span>
      <h1 class="mb-4 font-headline text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tighter text-white md:text-6xl">
        Projenizi Birlikte <br /><span class="text-secondary-container">Hayata Geçirelim</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-primary-fixed-dim">
        Güneş enerjisi, EV şarj veya danışmanlık konularında uzman ekibimiz size en uygun çözümü sunmak için hazır.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-surface-container-low px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl grid-cols-1 items-start gap-16 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <span class="mb-4 block text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">
          İletişim Kanalları
        </span>
        <h2 class="mb-8 font-headline text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">
          Size nasıl yardımcı olabiliriz?
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-container">location_on</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">Adres</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-on-surface">Türkiye</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
                Saha ziyaretleri tüm illerde gerçekleştirilmektedir.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-container">mail</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">E-Posta</div>
              <a
                href="mailto:info@solutenerji.com"
                class="font-semibold text-primary transition-colors hover:text-secondary"
              >
                info@solutenerji.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary-container">schedule</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="mb-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">Çalışma Saatleri</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-on-surface">Pazartesi – Cuma: 09:00 – 18:00</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Acil teknik destek için 7/24 ulaşabilirsiniz.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-lowest p-8">
          <h3 class="mb-4 font-headline text-lg font-bold text-primary">Neden Solut Enerji?</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-secondary-container"
                style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >
                check_circle
              </span>
              500+ tamamlanan proje deneyimi
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-secondary-container"
                style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >
                check_circle
              </span>
              Anahtar teslim çözümler, mühendislikten kuruluma
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-secondary-container"
                style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >
                check_circle
              </span>
              24/7 teknik destek
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
              <span
                class="material-symbols-outlined text-base text-secondary-container"
                style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;"
              >
                check_circle
              </span>
              %99 müşteri memnuniyeti
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="mb-2 font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary">Ücretsiz Teklif Alın</h3>
        <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Formu doldurun, en kısa sürede size dönelim.</p>

        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/FORM_ID_HERE" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Solut Enerji - Yeni İletişim Talebi" />

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">
                Ad Soyad *
              </label>
              <input
                name="ad_soyad"
                type="text"
                required
                placeholder="Ad Soyad"
                class="w-full border-0 border-b border-outline-variant bg-transparent py-3 text-sm text-on-surface transition-colors placeholder-outline focus:border-primary focus:ring-0"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <label class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">
                Telefon
              </label>
              <input
                name="telefon"
                type="tel"
                placeholder="+90 5xx xxx xx xx"
                class="w-full border-0 border-b border-outline-variant bg-transparent py-3 text-sm text-on-surface transition-colors placeholder-outline focus:border-primary focus:ring-0"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">
              E-Posta Adresi *
            </label>
            <input
              name="email"
              type="email"
              required
              placeholder="email@adresiniz.com"
              class="w-full border-0 border-b border-outline-variant bg-transparent py-3 text-sm text-on-surface transition-colors placeholder-outline focus:border-primary focus:ring-0"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">
              Hizmet Türü
            </label>
            <select
              name="hizmet_turu"
              class="w-full border-0 border-b border-outline-variant bg-transparent py-3 text-sm text-on-surface transition-colors focus:border-primary focus:ring-0"
            >
              <option value="">Seçiniz...</option>
              <option value="mesken_ges">Mesken Çatı GES Kurulumu</option>
              <option value="ev_sarj">EV Şarj İstasyonu</option>
              <option value="ges_danismanlik">GES Danışmanlık</option>
              <option value="diger">Diğer</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="font-label text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">
              Mesajınız *
            </label>
            <textarea
              name="mesaj"
              required
              rows="4"
              placeholder="Projeniz hakkında kısaca bilgi verin..."
              class="w-full resize-none border-0 border-b border-outline-variant bg-transparent py-3 text-sm text-on-surface transition-colors placeholder-outline focus:border-primary focus:ring-0"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-2">
            <button
              type="submit"
              class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-secondary-container py-4 font-headline font-extrabold text-on-secondary-fixed transition-all hover:opacity-90 active:scale-95"
            >
              <span>Mesajı Gönder</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">send</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="text-center text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant">
            Gönder butonuna basarak <a href="#" class="underline">Gizlilik Politikamızı</a> kabul etmiş olursunuz.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
